sub_title: PhD candidate & Data Steward at UMCG
summary:
I am a PhD candidate at University Medical Center Groningen. My PhD project focuses on understanding self-control development in children and adolescents using a biopsychosocial approach.

- Information about my publications: https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term=Yugyun+Kim
- Information about pre-registered research plans: https://osf.io/2nmfw/
